<li id="cite_note-25"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-25">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><a href="/w/index.php?title=Jassuda_B%C3%A9darride&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Jassuda Bédarride (page does not exist)">Jassuda Bédarride</a>, <i>Les Juifs en France,</i> pp.&#160;49, 454, note 21; <a href="/wiki/Jacques_Basnage" title="Jacques Basnage">Jacques Basnage</a>, <i>Histoire des Juifs</i>, iv. 1212; <a href="/w/index.php?title=P._Cassel&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="P. Cassel (page does not exist)">P. Cassel</a>, <i>Juden</i>, in <a href="/wiki/Ersch" class="mw-redirect" title="Ersch">Ersch</a> and <a href="/wiki/Johann_Gottfried_Gruber" title="Johann Gottfried Gruber">Gruber</a>'s "Encyc." pp.&#160;16, 17; 52, note 78; 67, notes 50 and 51; 115, 171, 224.</span>
